commit.title: [api] Move `Vernacexpr` to parsing.
commit.message:
[api] Move `Vernacexpr` to parsing.

There were some spurious dependencies on the `Vernac` AST in the
pretyper, to this purpose, we slice out the bits that indeed are
defined by the lower layers, and finally place `Vernacexpr` in its
proper place.

Note that still the core AST has to be placed in the elaborator
[pretyper] and this is the main client.

Also, `interp` still depends on `Parsing.Extend`, by means of
`Notation_term` this is unfortunate but not critical.

Moved types:

- `universe_decl_expr`: to `Univdecls`
- `hint_info_expr`, `hint_info_gen`: to `Typeclasses`
- `opacity_flag`: to `Proof_global`
- `proof_bullet`: to `Proof_bullet`
- `goal_selector`: to `Goal_select`
